WEBVTT

00:01.668 --> 00:04.971
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:04.971 --> 00:08.224
Boy, did I have a
crazy dream last night.

00:08.224 --> 00:09.175
What was it?

00:09.175 --> 00:11.644
I was at this party with
a bunch of strangers.

00:11.644 --> 00:14.147
The food was great. The music was loud.

00:14.147 --> 00:15.648
All of a sudden,

00:15.648 --> 00:17.650
everybody in the place
stopped and was lookin' at me,

00:17.650 --> 00:19.652
and I realized that I
wasn't wearing any pants.

00:19.652 --> 00:20.653
Oh, yes, yes.

00:20.653 --> 00:23.156
I've had that dream a million times.

00:23.156 --> 00:25.859
Yeah, me, too, and boy, is
it ever embarrassing, huh?

00:25.859 --> 00:27.277
Why is that?

00:31.414 --> 00:33.783
Uh... uh, Norm?

00:33.783 --> 00:35.285
Never embarrassed me.

00:35.285 --> 00:36.202
Tell you the one I hate.

00:36.202 --> 00:38.204
You know, you're back in college, right?

00:38.204 --> 00:40.206
And you haven't been to
class the entire semester,

00:40.206 --> 00:42.208
and the teacher's about
to give the final exam.

00:42.208 --> 00:43.710
Oh, yeah, that one's the worst.

00:43.710 --> 00:45.211
What're you talkin' about, Carla?

00:45.211 --> 00:46.379
You never went to college.

00:46.379 --> 00:48.631
It's a dream, stupid.

00:50.300 --> 00:54.354
Well, how about the one where
you go to this fancy restaurant,

00:54.354 --> 00:55.355
and before they let you in,

00:55.355 --> 00:56.856
they make you leave
your legs at the door?

00:59.359 --> 01:02.362
Then the girl gives you
claim check number six.

01:02.362 --> 01:03.730
So you go in,

01:03.730 --> 01:05.065
but instead of food,

01:05.065 --> 01:07.067
everyone's eatin' their silverware.

01:07.067 --> 01:08.568
Only you can't really enjoy your fork

01:08.568 --> 01:10.070
because you're so worried

01:10.070 --> 01:12.572
that whoever got claim check
number nine might finish first

01:12.572 --> 01:14.958
and pick up your legs by mistake.

01:18.244 --> 01:20.130
Yeah, oh, yeah.

01:22.132 --> 01:26.086
(piano plays)

01:26.086 --> 01:28.505
? Making your way in the world today ?

01:28.505 --> 01:31.508
? Takes everything you've got ?

01:31.508 --> 01:34.010
? Taking a break from all your worries ?

01:34.010 --> 01:37.013
? Sure would help a lot ?

01:37.013 --> 01:42.519
? Wouldn't you like to get away? ?

01:42.519 --> 01:45.438
? Sometimes you want to go ?

01:45.438 --> 01:50.944
? Where everybody knows your name ?

01:50.944 --> 01:55.448
? And they're always glad you came ?

01:55.448 --> 01:57.951
? You want to be where you can see ?

01:57.951 --> 02:00.453
? Our troubles are all the same ?

02:00.453 --> 02:05.959
? You want to be where
everybody knows your name ?

02:05.959 --> 02:08.461
? You want to go where people know ?

02:08.461 --> 02:10.964
? People are all the same ?

02:10.964 --> 02:15.468
? You want to go where
everybody knows your name. ?

